services:
  frontend:
    image: ghcr.io/bishko86/descartes-square-frontend:latest

    restart: unless-stopped
    ports:
      - "80:80"
    depends_on:
      - api
    networks:
      - app-network

  api:
    image: ghcr.io/bishko86/descartes-square-api:latest
    restart: unless-stopped
    env_file: .env
    environment:
      DATABASE_CONNECTION: mongodb://mongodb:27017/descartes-square
      PORT: 3000
    depends_on:
      - mongodb
    networks:
      - app-network

  mongodb:
    image: mongo:7
    restart: unless-stopped
    volumes:
      - mongodb_data:/data/db
    networks:
      - app-network

volumes:
  mongodb_data:

networks:
  app-network:
    driver: bridge
